Event.find_or_create_by(name: "Elevated Weirdo Game Show & Ragbag Productions Sideshow!", date_and_time: DateTime.parse("Saturday, February 9, 2019 at 9 PM – 12 AM"), location: "Monstercade", organizer: "Monstercade", description: "WE'RE BACK! Free door prizes for first 20 paying people at the door!\nAnyone can play! Win fabulous prizes!\nWhere clown babes roam and dangerous dames tease you...Ragbag Productions is back at Monstercade! Join us for a night of sideshow, comedy and a live game show!!\nFeaturing nationally touring performers and hometown favorites!\n\nFEATURING...\nElevated Weirdo Game Show\nA woman both mystifying & lethal, Bette Machete\nThe mistress of whimsy, Scarlett Storm\nThe funniest woman in town, Cabell Wilkinson\n\nDoors at 8 pm | Show at 9 pm\n$7 admission\nBring cash for tipping & merch!\n\n***SHOW GUIDELINES***\n-This is an interactive show. The performers will interact with you and may touch you.\n-Please return any articles of clothing to a staff\nmember or performer.\n-Please do not touch the performers.\n-Remember to tip! This is what many of us do for a living.\n-Most importantly, hoot and holler when you see something you like and HAVE FUN!", event_url: "https://www.facebook.com/events/745324949139215/")
